g(x,y,z)= \begin{cases} \frac{xy+xz+yz}{\sqrt(x^2+y^2+z^2)}, & \text{if } xi+yj+zk \neq 0 \\ 0, & \text{if } xi+yj+zk = 0 \\ \end{cases} 
\partial_xg(0)
\partial_yg(0)
\partial_zg(0)
\partial
 \partial_xg(0,0,0)=\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{g(x,0,0)-g(0,0,0)}{x}= \lim_{x\to 0}\frac{0+0+0}{x\sqrt {x^2+0+0}}=0. 
